  "prompt": "Why is Llaollao (the frozen yoghurt brand) so popular in Singapore at the moment?",
  "response": "Llaollao gained significant popularity in Singapore due to several factors:\n\n1. Unique product offering\n- Healthy frozen yogurt alternative to traditional ice cream\n- Customizable toppings and sauces\n- Perceived as a trendy and Instagram-worthy dessert\n\n2. Social media marketing\n- Strong social media presence\n- Attractive, colorful presentations that are appealing on platforms like Instagram\n- Encouraged customers to share their creations online\n\n3. Pricing and promotions\n- Competitive pricing\n- Frequent promotional offers and discounts\n- Attractive loyalty programs\n\n4. Cultural fit\n- Health-conscious trend in Singapore\n- Appealing to younger demographics who value aesthetically pleasing food\n- Matching Singaporeans' love for desserts and trying new food trends\n\n5. Strategic expansion\n- Rapid store openings across Singapore\n- Located in convenient locations like shopping malls\n- Quick service and convenient format\n\nWhile Llaollao was incredibly popular around 2015-2017, its popularity has since fluctuated. The brand experienced challenges and some store closures, but it remains recognizable in Singapore's dessert scene.\n\nThese factors contributed to its initial surge in popularity and widespread appeal among Singaporeans.",
